name: North Carolina
notes: North Carolina uses both 0 and O in different positions. Current plates have ABC-1234 format with 'First in Flight' slogan and Wright Flyer graphic. County information appears on small stickers or tabs. O only used on Outer Banks (OBX) special tags.
